Class KontaktDeviceServiceStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.connection.KontaktDeviceServiceStore

    • Constructor Detail

      • KontaktDeviceServiceStore

        public KontaktDeviceServiceStore(List<android.bluetooth.BluetoothGattService> gattServices,
                                 KontaktDeviceServiceStore.StoreType storeType)
                          throws android.os.RemoteException
        Instantiates a new Service store. If services sent are not compatible with the ones propagated by kontakt.io beacons(services list does not contain all required services: Service 1, Service 2, Service 3, Service 4, Service 5, Service 6, Service 7) then the RemoteException (informing that the beacon is not a property of kontakt.io) is thrown.
        Parameters:
        gattServices - beacon services list
        storeType - store type
        Throws:
        android.os.RemoteException - the remote exception thrown if services list does not match the specification of kontakt.io beacon
